data.description: Welcome to this stunning family home located in the desirable Maumelle Valley Estates. Step inside and you'll immediately notice the new carpet that has been installed throughout the entire house, giving it a fresh and inviting feel. The HVAC system is brand new, ensuring optimal comfort year-round. The roof was also recently replaced in 2022, providing peace of mind for years to come. The kitchen is equipped with brand new appliances, including a microwave and stove, making meal preparation a breeze. The open floor plan downstairs features a kitchen/living combo, perfect for entertaining, and there is a separate private dining room off the kitchen for more formal gatherings. Upstairs, you'll find three bedrooms and a full bathroom with two sinks, providing ample space for the whole family. The master suite is conveniently located downstairs and includes an additional half bathroom. The open style kitchen and living area create a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for hosting friends and family. With quick access to Maumelle BLVD, you'll have easy access to all the amenities the area has to offer. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity.
